# Content Rules

## Blog posts (`src/content/blog/`)

Frontmatter: `title`, `date`, `locale` (ru/en/pl), `tags`, `description`, `toc` (boolean), `translations` (optional map of locale -> slug).

File naming: `kebab-case.mdx`. One file per article (not per locale, unless translated).

## Pages (`src/content/pages/`)

Frontmatter: `title`, `locale`, `updated` (optional date).

File naming: `name.locale.mdx` (e.g. `about.en.mdx`, `now.ru.mdx`).

## Things (`src/content/things/`)

Frontmatter: `title`, `locale`, `thingId`, `description`, `tags`, `links` (array with `label`, `href`, optional `ruOnly`), `order`.

File naming: `thingId-locale.mdx` (e.g. `goh-en.mdx`). Use hyphen, NOT dot — dot causes Astro glob loader ID collisions.

## General

- Use JSX comments `{/* */}` in MDX, not HTML comments `<!-- -->`.
- Author name in English: "Vitaly Lyutarevich". In Polish: "Witalis Lutorowicz". In Russian: "Виталий Лютаревич".
- Never publish internal company data (employee names, portal links, budgets) in blog articles.
